1
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:34,990
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:37,960
[Episode 27]

3
00:01:47,789 --> 00:01:48,650
Your Highness,

4
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:50,870
His Majesty prepared these clothes
beforehand

5
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:52,430
for us to conceal our identities.

6
00:01:52,430 --> 00:01:53,690
Let me help you change.

7
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,590
When did he start planning all this?

8
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,620
Your Highness,

9
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,590
please eat something.

10
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:05,120
We need to hit the road soon.

11
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,210
I'm not leaving.

12
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:11,680
We'll return to the palace
at the crack of dawn.

13
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,630
By His Majesty's decree,

14
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:15,100
if Your Highness asks to return,

15
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:16,900
we can use our lives as leverage.

16
00:02:23,230 --> 00:02:25,360
He knows I won't take an innocent life,

17
00:02:27,910 --> 00:02:29,710
so he devised this tactic for me.

18
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:33,520
Fine.

19
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,650
You are all free now.

20
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,600
Let's part ways here.

21
00:02:44,870 --> 00:02:45,730
Your Highness!

22
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,240
What?

23
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,800
Are you going to tie me up?

24
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,120
Your Highness...

25
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:54,800
Upon departure,

26
00:02:54,970 --> 00:02:56,970
His Majesty left me with this letter

27
00:02:57,870 --> 00:03:01,400
and asked me to give it to Your Highness
after we escaped danger.

28
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,310
But now I'm taking the liberty
to present it

29
00:03:03,310 --> 00:03:04,370
ahead of schedule.

30
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,930
Your Highness, please read it over

31
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,420
before making a decision.

32
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,940
To my dear wife Wanyin:

33
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:18,110
My real name is Zhang San.

34
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:21,360
Laugh if you want.

35
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,160
In the past, I was often asked

36
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,520
why my parents gave me

37
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:27,610
such an unremarkable name.

38
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,190
But the reality was quite the opposite.

39
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:32,110
From elementary to middle school,

40
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:32,750
I was always the first student

41
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,960
whose name was remembered by the teachers.

42
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:37,350
[Zhang San]

43
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,190
However,

44
00:03:36,870 --> 00:03:38,530
except for this unusual name,

45
00:03:39,210 --> 00:03:40,340
everything about me

46
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:41,960
actually seemed lackluster.

47
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:45,470
[SOS]

48
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,340
I was only an average student.

49
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:50,850
At this point, you might start wondering

50
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:54,430
why I keep talking about my time
in junior high school.

51
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:56,690
That's because my life

52
00:03:57,790 --> 00:03:59,790
in the world we're from ended there.

53
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,050
In ninth grade,

54
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:04,920
when I was fiddling with my phone
in class,

55
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:06,240
ia pop-up add

56
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,590
sucked me into this book.

57
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,430
It has been 16 years and 8 months
since then.

58
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,019
Come to think of it,

59
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:19,240
I've been playing the role of Xiahou Dan

60
00:04:20,269 --> 00:04:22,930
for a longer time
than I spent on being Zhang San.

61
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:28,480
Long live Your Majesty!

62
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,000
In the past two years,

63
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:33,560
sometimes a doubt would cross my mind—

64
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,680
did that world outside the book

65
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,680
truly exist,

66
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:41,250
or was it just an illusion
created within my sick brain?

67
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:44,570
You know what's funny?

68
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,680
When I first arrived,

69
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:48,830
I felt like I was trapped

70
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:50,490
in a never-ending nightmare.

71
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:52,530
But now in retrospect,

72
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,630
I can barely recall the name

73
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:56,030
of my junior high school.

74
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,409
It all changed when you asked,

75
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,600
"How

76
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:01,870
are

77
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:02,830
you?"

78
00:05:04,070 --> 00:05:06,070
I finally realized my past was true,

79
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:08,830
and that I had

80
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:10,510
had a real life.

81
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:12,930
I once had parents,

82
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,390
friends,

83
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,190
and a future.

84
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:20,890
I'm such a despicable man.

85
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,520
You saved me at that very moment,

86
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,180
yet in the next second,

87
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,650
I devised a plan to deceive you,

88
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:29,780
to gain your trust,

89
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,090
to become your ally,

90
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,850
and to use your knowledge of the script

91
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,100
for my own benefit.

92
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,360
Only through that

93
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,620
could I achieve victory in the surest way

94
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,570
and retaliate on the Empress Dowager

95
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,920
and Prince Duan.

96
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:49,310
Don't worry, CEO Dan.

97
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,000
We're in the same boat to begin with.

98
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:54,220
I'll stick with you till the very end.

99
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,659
In front of you,

100
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:58,680
I've not only glossed over my past,

101
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:02,430
but also carefully watched
my manners and speech,

102
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:03,870
trying to act like

103
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:06,000
a modern person you're familiar with.

104
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,550
So what if you're the Emperor?

105
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:18,210
Can you protect her from harm?

106
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,650
That I can do.

107
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:21,070
Then can you guarantee

108
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:23,430
that among all the women in the world,
she'll be the only one you want?

109
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:24,430
That's also easy.

110
00:06:26,170 --> 00:06:27,240
As Zhang San,

111
00:06:28,090 --> 00:06:30,350
loving you seems to be a matter of course.

112
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,800
But as Xiahou Dan,

113
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,460
it's practically insane.

114
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:39,290
I can't tell
when exactly I fell in love with you.

115
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:41,150
The only thing I'm sure of

116
00:06:41,290 --> 00:06:42,820
is that I became more afraid

117
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,890
of exposing the truth thereafter.

118
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:48,880
Wanyin,

119
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,170
believe it or not,

120
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,080
only when I reverted to being

121
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:57,390
Zhang San from Xiahou Dan in front of you

122
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:01,190
did it occur to me, little by little,

123
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:04,880
that how far I had drifted
from my original identity.

124
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,260
You came here too late,

125
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:07,960
Wanyin.

126
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:09,240
♪ Tell me ♪

127
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:13,360
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

128
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,450
There isn't a fellow of yours
waiting for you.

129
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,970
You have to stuck with me,

130
00:07:14,970 --> 00:07:16,120
♪ Walk past me ♪

131
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,510
a crazy dying man.

132
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:20,300
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

133
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:21,630
Those who are drowning

134
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:24,050
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

135
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,920
all wish for a piece of driftwood.

136
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,640
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

137
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,840
But when they are too far from shore,

138
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,370
they're destined for doom.

139
00:07:28,370 --> 00:07:34,230
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

140
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,770
By holding onto the driftwood,

141
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,630
they will only end up dragging it

142
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:33,960
down into the water too.

143
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:36,020
You shouldn't let love

144
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:36,400
♪ Blame me ♪

145
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,360
cloud your judgement.

146
00:07:36,970 --> 00:07:40,570
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

147
00:07:38,570 --> 00:07:40,700
She's driftwood to me, a drowning man.

148
00:07:41,290 --> 00:07:41,930
I hope I can

149
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:43,310
♪ Hide me ♪

150
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,650
at least keep your hands free of blood.

151
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:47,630
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

152
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:46,880
In this living hell,

153
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,420
there should at least be a place

154
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:51,510
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

155
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:52,330
for you to have a sound sleep.

156
00:07:52,330 --> 00:07:54,930
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

157
00:07:52,810 --> 00:07:54,170
[Taiji Hall]

158
00:07:53,610 --> 00:07:54,360
All I beg for

159
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:56,750
is to delay facing

160
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:58,810
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

161
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,280
the fear and wariness in your eyes.

162
00:07:58,860 --> 00:08:01,030
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

163
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,310
I wish for nothing

164
00:08:01,370 --> 00:08:03,750
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

165
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,560
but to see you always thriving
like burning fire

166
00:08:03,810 --> 00:08:05,680
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

167
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,510
and shining like the moon.

168
00:08:05,710 --> 00:08:08,180
♪ I never yielded ♪

169
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,270
We need to play

170
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,960
♪ But why ♪

171
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,630
a game of survival overtime.

172
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:11,160
I hope you will remain to be the brave

173
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:14,660
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

174
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:12,600
and fearless young lady

175
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,130
who I met in the first place.

176
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,240
Punch the Empress Dowager

177
00:08:15,140 --> 00:08:17,510
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

178
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:16,510
and kick Prince Duan!

179
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,680
Even if he were truly a god,

180
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,360
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

181
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,920
I would never surrender!

182
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:21,740
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

183
00:08:20,310 --> 00:08:21,110
Let's get him!

184
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,310
I am not alone on this path!

185
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:23,980
♪ The first time I met you ♪

186
00:08:22,850 --> 00:08:23,360
Wanyin,

187
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,310
I no longer have a place to call home.

188
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:33,740
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

189
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:28,410
But in you, I've found my home.

190
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:31,060
If you ever fear and waiver,

191
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:34,270
or need support from a fellow of yours,

192
00:08:35,409 --> 00:08:36,870
I'll gladly play that role

193
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,630
till the day

194
00:08:39,909 --> 00:08:41,020
my life is over.

195
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,510
I beg you, Mr. Bei,

196
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,740
to treat her

197
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,360
as you'd treat me.

198
00:08:45,860 --> 00:08:47,210
Please ensure her safety at all costs.

199
00:08:47,210 --> 00:08:48,410
♪ Blame me ♪

200
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,490
What I didn't expect

201
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:50,230
was that this day would come so soon.

202
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:52,540
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

203
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:54,160
I will try my best tomorrow.

204
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,220
♪ Hide me ♪

205
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:55,510
If I succeed,

206
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:59,700
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

207
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,250
the burden on you

208
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,370
will be lighter.

209
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,720
If I fail,

210
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:03,450
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

211
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,240
do as the final page says.

212
00:09:04,310 --> 00:09:06,920
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

213
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:08,680
You should be able to make an escape
that way.

214
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:10,850
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

215
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:11,330
Then you will have to

216
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:13,020
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

217
00:09:12,730 --> 00:09:13,940
tread the road ahead alone.

218
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,860
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

219
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,670
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

220
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:18,480
It's going to be a long

221
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:20,220
♪ I never yielded ♪

222
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:20,630
and dangerous journey.

223
00:09:20,530 --> 00:09:22,050
♪ But why ♪

224
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:22,510
Be extra careful.

225
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:26,750
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

226
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:26,050
I'm sorry for not being

227
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,400
a good enough person.

228
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:29,520
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

229
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:30,350
Though I've lied to you many times,

230
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,410
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

231
00:09:31,450 --> 00:09:33,780
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

232
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,050
this apology

233
00:09:34,250 --> 00:09:35,950
♪ The first time I met you ♪

234
00:09:34,420 --> 00:09:35,550
is genuine and true.

235
00:09:36,540 --> 00:09:39,470
♪ There was once light ♪

236
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:39,480
You're the bravest

237
00:09:40,060 --> 00:09:48,460
♪ In my soul ♪

238
00:09:42,370 --> 00:09:44,100
and the most formidable person

239
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:46,880
I've met in my two lives.

240
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:50,980
You'll definitely have the last laugh,

241
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:52,030
fighting your way

242
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,040
to a bright new world.

243
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:56,960
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

244
00:09:55,370 --> 00:09:56,080
By then,

245
00:09:57,010 --> 00:09:58,770
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

246
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,800
should you have forgiven me,

247
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:01,380
♪ I never yielded ♪

248
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,780
just enjoy a hot pot

249
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:02,960
on holidays and festivals,

250
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:03,140
♪ But why ♪

251
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:08,020
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

252
00:10:05,330 --> 00:10:06,790
as if I were there with you.

253
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:10,690
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

254
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,680
From: Zhang San.

255
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,570
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

256
00:10:12,610 --> 00:10:14,940
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

257
00:10:15,410 --> 00:10:17,190
♪ The first time I met you ♪

258
00:10:17,710 --> 00:10:25,590
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

259
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:37,790
Hurry up.

260
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,120
His Majesty suddenly fell ill.

261
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,240
Physicians, please be quick!

262
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:40,870
Sure, sure.

263
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:41,270
Got it.

264
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:52,000
Move faster, physicians.

265
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:54,960
My leg!

266
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,120
Hurry!

267
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,840
It's not His Majesty.

268
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,300
This...

269
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,540
is not His Majesty.

270
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:14,490
Say that again, I dare you!

271
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:18,630
What are you all waiting for?

272
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,020
Come fix my leg right now!

273
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,390
Yes, yes.

274
00:11:23,050 --> 00:11:23,820
Quick!

275
00:11:37,230 --> 00:11:38,090
Your Highness,

276
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:40,360
Chu Si scouted the gate tower at night

277
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:42,960
and found the Imperial Guards
to be led by Prince Duan's men.

278
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,390
Now,

279
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:46,280
the city gate is surrounded
by border troops.

280
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:49,430
As for where we should go,

281
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,840
it's up to Your Highness.

282
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,260
How are your injuries?

283
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:55,090
These minor wounds

284
00:11:55,270 --> 00:11:56,330
amount to nothing.

285
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,600
Let's leave the mountain

286
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,320
for an inhabited area.

287
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:05,190
Or we can't receive news
about the capital.

288
00:12:05,190 --> 00:12:07,030
I'm here to protect Your Highness
by imperial order.

289
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,510
There are many uncertainties now.

290
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:10,030
The troops from three border regions
arranged by Prince Duan

291
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:11,270
are closing in on this place

292
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:12,440
to suppress the Imperial Guards

293
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,040
and help him take the throne.

294
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:15,490
These troops

295
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:18,490
are coming from the north, east and south.

296
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,240
I suggest

297
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,100
we find a way out

298
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:22,840
before they join forces.

299
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,840
Let's head south.

300
00:12:24,210 --> 00:12:25,070
Your Highness,

301
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:27,470
the Right Army is coming from the south.

302
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:28,440
We'll head south

303
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,740
to Peiyang.

304
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,930
That's what His Majesty wants.

305
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:37,250
Clothes were prepared beforehand, right?

306
00:12:37,250 --> 00:12:38,110
Put them on now.

307
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:39,870
Then we'll set out.

308
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:40,200
Yes.

309
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,510
Yes.

310
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:33,390
Sir,

311
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:35,470
did you sell fish in town today?

312
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,190
Yes.

313
00:13:36,330 --> 00:13:37,630
The business wasn't good,

314
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:38,760
so I came back early.

315
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:40,510
Ma'am,

316
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:42,070
is your husband home?

317
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,750
Yes, he is.

318
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:46,480
There's a huge manhunt in town now.

319
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:48,200
It's said to be complete chaos.

320
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,400
How weird and creepy.

321
00:13:50,150 --> 00:13:53,340
Why would so many people die
during the Empress Dowager's funeral?

322
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,670
Could it be possible that Her Majesty

323
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:55,990
tried to take people with her

324
00:13:55,990 --> 00:13:58,240
to the nether world
so she could have servants there?

325
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,370
But as I heard, it was

326
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,870
the demonic consort
who murdered the Empress Dowager

327
00:14:00,870 --> 00:14:01,750
and planned to kill

328
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:03,240
the Emperor too during the funeral.

329
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,280
Is that true?

330
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:06,670
There are wanted posters for her
at the city gate now.

331
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:08,600
-Really?
-It can't be fake, can it?

332
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,680
Excuse me.

333
00:14:12,630 --> 00:14:14,910
My sisters and I are heading
to the capital to meet our kin.

334
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:17,040
We just overheard your conversation.

335
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,490
Is it safe to go

336
00:14:18,670 --> 00:14:19,730
to the capital now?

337
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,260
At a time like this,

338
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,000
even a strong male like me

339
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,530
dare not enter the capital.

340
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,940
Young ladies, I suggest

341
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,500
you make a second plan.

342
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,600
Right now, entry to the capital

343
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,330
is allowed, but exit is denied.

344
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:36,960
My husband went there to sell fish
early in the day,

345
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,870
and is still trapped within till now.

346
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:40,730
But this gentleman here just said

347
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:43,340
the manhunt was for the demonic consort.

348
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:44,390
Why are even males

349
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:47,240
forbidden to leave the capital now?

350
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:49,150
Who knows?

351
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:51,130
Come on. Let's go home.

352
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:58,720
Could it be

353
00:14:59,670 --> 00:15:01,270
that Xiahou Dan has escaped?

354
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:16,870
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness!

355
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:17,200
Your Highness!

356
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:18,130
Are you alright?

357
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:20,780
You're burning up.

358
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,410
We can't go any further.

359
00:15:22,510 --> 00:15:24,480
Her Highness needs to take a rest
somewhere.

360
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:25,630
I'll check out on that house.

361
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:26,160
Don't.

362
00:15:26,690 --> 00:15:28,620
Commoners dread strange men most.

363
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:30,610
And there are so many of us.

364
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:32,270
Chu Wu, you do it instead.

365
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:33,310
The two of you,

366
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,860
go hide somewhere.

367
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:38,910
Take care of Her Highness.

368
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:39,240
Sure.

369
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,370
Let's go.

370
00:15:52,250 --> 00:15:52,840
Sir,

371
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,270
we plan to visit our relatives
in the capital.

372
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:57,200
Yet our money was stolen on the way.

373
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:59,220
Now, the lady of our house is sick.

374
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:02,890
This is all the money we have on us.

375
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:05,050
Could you kindly give us some food?

376
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,730
We're all suffering souls.

377
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:08,140
Come on in.

378
00:16:09,790 --> 00:16:10,320
Let's go.

379
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,200
Thank you.

380
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:28,090
Why is your wife...

381
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:29,800
burning that?

382
00:16:31,270 --> 00:16:33,800
To mourn her brother
who lived near Mount Bei.

383
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,870
Yesterday,

384
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,910
while he was taking a peek

385
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:39,080
at the Empress Dowager's funeral,

386
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:40,580
unexpectedly,

387
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,850
Prince Duan rose in a rebellion

388
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,770
and caused many deaths.

389
00:16:44,790 --> 00:16:47,050
My wife's brother somehow lost his life.

390
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,580
Prince Duan started a rebellion?

391
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,080
Was it a success?

392
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:52,750
W-We...

393
00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:54,550
have no idea at all.

394
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,790
He who delivered the bad news to us

395
00:16:56,790 --> 00:16:58,320
just said many people died,

396
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,550
most of which were Imperial Guards.

397
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:02,720
He didn't know much other than that.

398
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:06,770
The dead were mostly Imperial Guards.

399
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:08,609
There was either an internal fight
within them,

400
00:17:08,609 --> 00:17:10,740
or that Prince Duan veiled his armies.

401
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:11,740
In either case,

402
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,420
CEO Dan must've got in grave danger.

403
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:14,880
My Lady.

404
00:17:15,310 --> 00:17:15,750
Sir,

405
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,270
we shouldn't bother you
at a time like this,

406
00:17:18,270 --> 00:17:19,920
but the lady of our house is severely ill.

407
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,440
Could you make her a bowl of noodles?

408
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,240
Wait a moment.

409
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,030
My love,

410
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,740
make some noodles now.

411
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,210
Let's go.

412
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:40,440
Here you are.

413
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,500
Have some noodles.

414
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:42,760
Thank you.

415
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:44,400
Take it.

416
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,030
Thanks.

417
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:53,450
Your Highness,

418
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,010
at least have a bite.

419
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:56,920
A long journey awaits us.

420
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:57,720
That's right.

421
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,590
Travel takes physical strength.

422
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:00,850
Please eat something.

423
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,000
You're right.

424
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,440
I can't fall now.

425
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:08,810
He's still waiting for me.

426
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,170
You should eat too.

427
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:13,030
Yes.

428
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,740
Alright, stop crying.

429
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:25,480
It's bad for your eyes.

430
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:28,070
I just pity my unfortunate brother.

431
00:18:31,030 --> 00:18:33,630
That heinous Prince Duan
is beneath contempt!

432
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,440
Keep it down.

433
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:42,000
First,
the Emperor killed the Empress Dowager.

434
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:45,200
Then, Prince Duan rebelled
and tried to kill the Emperor.

435
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,010
These...

436
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:48,300
are all royal affairs.

437
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:50,110
How could we have foreseen those?

438
00:18:50,110 --> 00:18:51,640
It's true I don't know much,

439
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,520
but my brother

440
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,310
told me...

441
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:56,270
that the Emperor ordered
equal land distribution

442
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:57,330
and tax reduction.

443
00:18:57,480 --> 00:19:00,340
His Majesty also executed
many corrupt officials!

444
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:03,110
Isn't it enough to put
these corrupt officials in jail?

445
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:04,110
Why execute them?

446
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:07,240
If I am to have the people's support,

447
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:09,250
I must first give them hope.

448
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:10,730
Execution is a just desert

449
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:12,700
for these vile officials.

450
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,970
It gives hope to the people.

451
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:17,510
Back then,

452
00:19:18,390 --> 00:19:20,650
I thought he was just acting over the top.

453
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:21,960
Little did I imagine

454
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:25,180
that after living for 16 years
in this world,

455
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:28,100
he had already seen
the harsh truths of life.

456
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:30,570
Sacrificing one person

457
00:19:31,310 --> 00:19:32,840
to ensure others' survival

458
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:34,590
is sometimes unavoidable.

459
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,550
Don't you forget

460
00:19:36,270 --> 00:19:37,600
they are 2D characters.

461
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:39,730
I would also remind myself

462
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:43,200
not to get too emotionally involved.

463
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:45,240
Do you really think you are a tyrant?

464
00:19:45,270 --> 00:19:46,720
I am a tyrant,

465
00:19:47,510 --> 00:19:48,980
as I have always been.

466
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:52,550
But the man who claimed to be a tyrant

467
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,370
and to have no regard for others' lives

468
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:57,440
is actually spending what little

469
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,590
time and life he has

470
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,350
to protect

471
00:20:00,350 --> 00:20:02,410
all those irrelevant 2D characters.

472
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,500
Your Highness,

473
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:10,240
don't cry.

474
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:22,750
What's with this lady?

475
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:26,410
Perhaps she's missing
her family in the capital.

476
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:30,000
Life hasn't treated us well.

477
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,110
Dear,

478
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,320
let me get you some more soup.

479
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:35,970
You won't feel homesick on a full stomach.

480
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:38,240
Thank you, ma'am.

481
00:20:39,550 --> 00:20:40,880
But I can't eat anymore.

482
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:45,780
Why is your face so red?

483
00:20:47,670 --> 00:20:48,960
She's running a high fever.

484
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:50,680
We need to get her a physician now.

485
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:51,350
Honey!

486
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:52,120
I'm fine.

487
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,800
I'm just tired from the journey.

488
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:57,630
Could we stay here for the night?

489
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:02,100
We don't mean to turn you down,

490
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:04,980
but the authorities have issued a notice

491
00:21:05,350 --> 00:21:07,550
forbidding residents
from housing strangers

492
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,270
overnight.

493
00:21:09,790 --> 00:21:11,070
Although you're not bad people,

494
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:11,790
ladies,

495
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:14,220
we common folks

496
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:16,570
dare not go against the authorities.

497
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:17,840
How about...

498
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:21,550
In that case,

499
00:21:22,830 --> 00:21:24,030
we'll take our leave.

500
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:26,340
Thank you for the noodles.

501
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:33,520
Thank you.

502
00:21:46,750 --> 00:21:47,070
That...

503
00:21:47,070 --> 00:21:48,000
What's going on?

504
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:48,490
This...

505
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:57,140
Well...

506
00:21:59,000 --> 00:21:59,660
Quiet down!

507
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:00,970
My Lady,

508
00:22:01,660 --> 00:22:03,560
she was just climbing
through the kitchen window

509
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:05,090
when I caught her in the act.

510
00:22:05,510 --> 00:22:06,170
Sir, ma'am,

511
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:08,790
take a look. Are these your belongings?

512
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:15,610
We saved this meat for the New Year.

513
00:22:16,290 --> 00:22:17,420
And that hairpin...

514
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:18,790
It seems to be Wang's.

515
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:19,880
Right.

516
00:22:22,590 --> 00:22:23,650
Easy on her, Chu Wu.

517
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:24,610
She's just a kid.

518
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:25,350
Yes.

519
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:30,160
Sir, ma'am,

520
00:22:31,430 --> 00:22:32,740
we bid you farewell.

521
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:34,030
This thief is yours

522
00:22:34,030 --> 00:22:34,760
to deal with.

523
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:36,640
Miss,

524
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,760
I wanted to say this earlier,

525
00:22:39,270 --> 00:22:41,010
but this old fool stopped me.

526
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:42,750
The authorities did issue a notice.

527
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:44,550
But our village is quite remote,

528
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:46,050
with the nearest inn

529
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:47,640
situated over 30 li away.

530
00:22:48,070 --> 00:22:49,830
It's not safe for you three ladies

531
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:50,920
to stay out there.

532
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:51,480
Yes.

533
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,360
Things have taken a turn.

534
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:55,550
They caught a thief for us.

535
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,460
Ladies, if you don't mind,

536
00:22:58,920 --> 00:23:00,650
please stay here for the night.

537
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:02,440
You may leave tomorrow morning.

538
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:03,070
Yes.

539
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:05,080
Good idea.

540
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:06,590
Thank you.

541
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,080
Come on. Get in the house.

542
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:12,000
Get up!

543
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:15,920
Move.

544
00:23:30,830 --> 00:23:31,690
Your Highness.

545
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:34,100
Your Highness?

546
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:38,270
When I escorted the thief to the woodshed,

547
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:39,480
she struggled too hard

548
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:40,610
and made much noise,

549
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:42,300
drawing some villagers over.

550
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:44,720
Our host returned the lost items
to his neighbors.

551
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:45,920
Now, about five to six households

552
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:47,120
are aware of our stay.

553
00:23:50,830 --> 00:23:51,690
Your Highness,

554
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:54,000
if we kill all those people
under the cover of darkness,

555
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,530
we can frame the thief for it

556
00:23:55,920 --> 00:23:57,380
and then cover our tracks.

557
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:57,880
No.

558
00:23:59,400 --> 00:23:59,930
Let's go.

559
00:24:00,270 --> 00:24:01,130
We should leave

560
00:24:01,590 --> 00:24:02,520
for Peiyang now.

561
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:06,210
Your Highness,

562
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:08,200
you're in no condition to go anywhere.

563
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,800
You need a good night's rest.

564
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:12,400
Chu Yi and Chu Si are keeping watch
on the roof.

565
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,460
We don't have to run

566
00:24:13,750 --> 00:24:15,150
until anyone reports us.

567
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:16,480
Fine.

568
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,340
I'll sleep a bit more then.

569
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:21,240
Wake me up in four hours.

570
00:24:22,110 --> 00:24:23,240
Yes, Your Highness.

571
00:24:28,940 --> 00:24:29,670
We found him!

572
00:24:35,070 --> 00:24:35,790
We found him,

573
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:36,450
Centurion.

574
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:37,800
Let me see.

575
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:41,830
It really is him.

576
00:24:42,510 --> 00:24:44,030
Shall we notify the Imperial Guards?

577
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,290
Are you stupid or what?

578
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,200
He was caught by us, the Central Army.

579
00:24:48,200 --> 00:24:49,350
Bring a few men with you

580
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:51,070
and escort him to His Highness.

581
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:51,350
Yes!

582
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:53,070
Take him away!

583
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:53,330
Yes!

584
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:54,490
Move!

585
00:24:58,590 --> 00:24:59,070
CEO Dan,

586
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,060
wait for me.

587
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:03,440
I'll be with you soon.

588
00:25:04,310 --> 00:25:05,170
Your Highness.

589
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,300
Your Highness!

590
00:25:07,110 --> 00:25:07,970
Your Highness.

591
00:25:09,750 --> 00:25:10,610
Your Highness,

592
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:12,480
there are soldiers here now.

593
00:25:14,750 --> 00:25:15,810
Search carefully!

594
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:17,000
Move!

595
00:25:17,270 --> 00:25:18,440
-Officer, are you mistaken?
-Darn it!

596
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:19,100
Officer...

597
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,900
They got to this place so soon.

598
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:23,050
Move!

599
00:25:25,510 --> 00:25:26,830
Cut the crap. Get a move on!

600
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:27,480
Be quick!

601
00:25:28,310 --> 00:25:28,790
Search the house!

602
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:29,520
Confess now!

603
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,550
I don't know anything.

604
00:25:32,550 --> 00:25:34,830
-Walk faster!
-Report the household
with suspicious lodgers

605
00:25:34,830 --> 00:25:35,560
immdiately!

606
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:37,440
The reward is10 tales of silver!

607
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:37,750
Officer!

608
00:25:37,750 --> 00:25:38,070
Your Highness!

609
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:39,720
-We're innocent!
-Your Highness!

610
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:40,030
Move!

611
00:25:40,030 --> 00:25:41,290
Use the rear door here.

612
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:41,880
Let's go.

613
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:42,730
Go there!

614
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:44,940
And you!

615
00:25:45,110 --> 00:25:46,040
-Hold on.
-Move!

616
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:51,450
Quickly!

617
00:25:52,790 --> 00:25:53,550
Confess now!

618
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:57,720
There are soldiers here.

619
00:25:57,720 --> 00:25:58,590
Run for your life.

620
00:25:58,590 --> 00:25:59,920
Don't steal again.

621
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:05,770
This way.

622
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:08,590
Check over there!

623
00:26:08,590 --> 00:26:08,920
Go!

624
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:13,830
Open the door!

625
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:14,620
Open up!

626
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:15,720
Who is it?

627
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,520
Open the door!

628
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:18,880
Now!

629
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:22,940
Search!

630
00:26:28,510 --> 00:26:29,370
Nobody's here.

631
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:30,320
Where is she?

632
00:26:30,590 --> 00:26:32,520
Did you tip her off and let her go?

633
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,620
Officer, we're innocent.

634
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:36,030
Officer,

635
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:37,830
we don't know who she really is.

636
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:40,050
She only asked to spend the night here.

637
00:26:40,790 --> 00:26:42,640
-Officer, please spare our lives.
-Don't hurt us.

638
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,170
Guys, go!

639
00:26:43,240 --> 00:26:44,400
Split up and search the village.

640
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:44,930
Go, guys!

641
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:46,550
Hurry!

642
00:26:51,940 --> 00:26:52,480
This way.

643
00:26:59,030 --> 00:26:59,890
It's a dead end.

644
00:27:00,310 --> 00:27:01,790
We need to first find an anchor up there

645
00:27:01,790 --> 00:27:03,850
and pull Your Highness up with a rope.

646
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:05,240
It's too late.

647
00:27:05,830 --> 00:27:07,560
The soldiers will be here soon.

648
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:08,640
Besides,

649
00:27:09,550 --> 00:27:10,610
how are we supposed

650
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,320
to find a long rope right now?

651
00:27:12,510 --> 00:27:14,110
We'll lure the soldiers away

652
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,590
to buy you as much time as possible.

653
00:27:15,590 --> 00:27:16,000
No.

654
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:19,220
You escaped by the skin of your teeth.

655
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,280
Going back

656
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,970
is no different than suicide.

657
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:26,290
Only I am their target.

658
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:27,640
You should leave.

659
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:29,240
I can't drag you down with me.

660
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,240
Your Highness...

661
00:27:30,270 --> 00:27:30,930
Just leave.

662
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:32,310
Don't worry, Your Highness.

663
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,480
We'll use the trees for cover,

664
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:34,640
take out some soldiers,

665
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:36,030
and kill ourselves before capture.

666
00:27:36,030 --> 00:27:37,760
We'll make sure no clue is left.

667
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:40,080
Exactly.

668
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:41,480
Chu Wu, Chu Qi,

669
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:42,450
think of a way

670
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:44,850
to help Her Highness out of danger.

671
00:27:46,510 --> 00:27:46,880
Wait.

672
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:49,910
What are your names?

673
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:51,330
We don't have names.

674
00:27:51,350 --> 00:27:52,720
"Chu Yi" and "Chu Si" sound good enough.

675
00:27:52,720 --> 00:27:54,180
Take care, Your Highness.

676
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,500
Do come back alive!

677
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,860
Your Highness,

678
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,200
death is almost certain.

679
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:01,640
Might as well take a gamble.

680
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,750
Chu Qi, stay alert.

681
00:28:02,970 --> 00:28:04,700
I'll go find an anchor up there.

682
00:28:10,790 --> 00:28:11,650
Your Highness,

683
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:13,430
let's take a rest over there.

684
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:29,200
I've been a liability to you all.

685
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:31,470
Don't beat yourself up, Your Highness.

686
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:33,410
Who's there?

687
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:56,650
Your Highness,

688
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,160
that hole's too small

689
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,690
to fit more than two people.

690
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,550
If she tries to harm you, I won't be able

691
00:29:01,550 --> 00:29:02,750
to rescue you in time.

692
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:06,050
She could've reported me for the reward,

693
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:08,130
yet she risked coming back for me.

694
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:10,010
I trust her.

695
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,880
You have great lightness skills.

696
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,340
Hide on the cliff face now.

697
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,000
Be careful.

698
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:15,400
Got it.

699
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:38,560
I saw them heading to the woods.

700
00:29:38,750 --> 00:29:40,080
Should we keep looking?

701
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,530
Of course we should.

702
00:29:41,790 --> 00:29:43,830
If we catch her,
we'll receive a thousand taels of silver

703
00:29:43,830 --> 00:29:44,890
and be set for life.

704
00:29:46,110 --> 00:29:48,040
That woman's quite good at hiding.

705
00:29:48,670 --> 00:29:50,400
How many villages have we searched?

706
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:51,640
I don't even get to enjoy the New Year.

707
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,570
Don't be afraid.

708
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:55,550
That's why she's called a demonic consort.

709
00:29:55,550 --> 00:29:56,510
The higher-ups

710
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:57,550
told us to catch her,

711
00:29:57,550 --> 00:29:58,680
be she alive or dead.

712
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:00,510
If she falls into our hands,

713
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:02,840
let's take her to bed
like the Emperor did!

714
00:30:03,790 --> 00:30:04,650
-Let's go!
-Go!

715
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,240
Check over there!

716
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:05,770
Go, guys!

717
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:25,880
You're unable to speak?

718
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:30,520
Now I understand

719
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,860
why you steal for a living.

720
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:03,830
Xiahou Dan.

721
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,440
Calling my name already, huh?

722
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:25,740
"Being ill,

723
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:28,960
the late Emperor felt
death was drawing near.

724
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:32,680
This edict was therefore made
to pass the throne to the Crown Prince.

725
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:34,540
But given the latter's minority,

726
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:38,240
Prince Duan is vested
the power to govern as regent."

727
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,930
Honorary titles

728
00:31:42,270 --> 00:31:43,550
are mere vanities.

729
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:46,330
Pick whatever you like, Your Majesty.

730
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:49,310
All is fine by me.

731
00:31:50,590 --> 00:31:52,630
Why don't you dress up
as the Empress Dowager

732
00:31:52,630 --> 00:31:53,860
in women's clothes?

733
00:31:55,070 --> 00:31:55,880
Xiahou Dan!

734
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,680
I forgot it.

735
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,430
You're scared of her.

736
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:04,080
What did you just say?

737
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:17,830
You knew clearly from the beginning

738
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,720
who harmed your mother

739
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,790
and you.

740
00:32:28,810 --> 00:32:31,140
But you had no choice
but to turn a blind eye

741
00:32:32,350 --> 00:32:33,860
and a deaf ear to the truth.

742
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:38,060
You decided to vent all your anger

743
00:32:39,350 --> 00:32:42,070
on an innocent person.

744
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:45,790
Why?

745
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:51,110
Because you were too weak.

746
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:56,770
You had to direct your hatred to someone,

747
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,530
or you couldn't have lived.

748
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:00,720
So,

749
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,590
you picked a soft target—

750
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:08,610
a headache sufferer,

751
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:12,070
and a mere puppet.

752
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,810
Luck was the entire reason

753
00:33:17,390 --> 00:33:19,570
that he ascended to the throne.

754
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:24,170
Given that, you, Xiahou Bo,

755
00:33:24,750 --> 00:33:26,410
feel the urge to tell the world

756
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,070
that you,

757
00:33:29,420 --> 00:33:30,410
Prince Duan,

758
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:35,200
are better than him in every way,

759
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:37,680
and that only you are

760
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:41,240
meant to be the ruler.

761
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:57,520
As a defeated loser

762
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:01,000
behind bars,

763
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,600
you're still talking tough.

764
00:34:05,420 --> 00:34:08,150
You're saying all this to provoke me,
aren't you?

765
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:10,510
It won't work, Xiahou Dan.

766
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:13,150
Stop struggling.

767
00:34:18,280 --> 00:34:20,080
I've hit a nerve with you, right?

768
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:20,719
Shut up!

769
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,219
Your Highness,

770
00:34:25,550 --> 00:34:26,480
I'll finish him.

771
00:34:27,070 --> 00:34:27,699
No need.

772
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:32,080
Make sure you rough the late Emperor up.

773
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:34,010
Remember

774
00:34:35,100 --> 00:34:36,900
to spare his right hand, though.

775
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:40,190
He needs it to write his final edict.

776
00:34:53,900 --> 00:34:54,580
Yang, I...

777
00:34:56,110 --> 00:34:56,639
I...

778
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:59,440
T-T-This is inappropriate.

779
00:35:02,550 --> 00:35:03,920
Er Lan, well, I...

780
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:04,710
I...

781
00:35:05,510 --> 00:35:06,320
I didn't mean to intrude.

782
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,120
I thought I entered Yang's room.

783
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,610
This room is more spacious,

784
00:35:12,670 --> 00:35:14,440
making it easier to attend to Cen.

785
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:16,050
So I swapped rooms with Yang this morning.

786
00:35:16,050 --> 00:35:16,710
Cen...

787
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:18,240
Cen...

788
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,490
Cen has arrived?

789
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:20,280
Not yet.

790
00:35:20,550 --> 00:35:22,280
Yang has set off to receive him.

791
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:26,760
Li, do you ever consider

792
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:29,070
stop standing in the cold wind
by the door?

793
00:35:29,070 --> 00:35:30,880
We've been through life and death
together.

794
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:32,540
Just forego the formalities.

795
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:45,360
Were you just saying

796
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:48,030
you had news about His Majesty?

797
00:35:48,030 --> 00:35:48,400
Yes.

798
00:35:50,710 --> 00:35:52,400
I waited at the palace gate all morning,

799
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,860
but still couldn't get in.

800
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:56,550
Nonetheless, a young eunuch
guarding the gate said

801
00:35:56,550 --> 00:35:59,760
Prince Duan summoned all ministers
to attend court tomorrow morning.

802
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:01,200
He's just a prince.

803
00:36:01,590 --> 00:36:03,450
What right does he have to do that?

804
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:05,670
I actually think it's a good thing.

805
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:06,480
Hell no!

806
00:36:11,070 --> 00:36:12,270
My apologies, Er Lan.

807
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:13,030
I...

808
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:16,600
I've got used to it.
I keep forgetting that you are...

809
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:21,090
In fact, I somewhat miss the time

810
00:36:21,710 --> 00:36:23,550
when you treated me like a man.

811
00:36:26,150 --> 00:36:27,460
We voiced our opinions

812
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,880
and argued till we were red in the face,

813
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:31,280
with the one and only focus

814
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:33,280
on offering counsel to His Majesty.

815
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:33,960
But now,

816
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:35,320
Wang is gone.

817
00:36:36,030 --> 00:36:37,430
Her Highness is missing.

818
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:39,240
His Majesty's fate is unknown.

819
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:40,530
Given that,

820
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:42,030
though this is not a fair request,

821
00:36:42,030 --> 00:36:43,360
I still have to ask you, Li,

822
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:45,960
to continue to conceal my identity
for a while.

823
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,800
Just treat me the same as before.

824
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:48,730
Sure.

825
00:36:51,710 --> 00:36:52,170
I got it.

826
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:57,600
I'll try my best.

827
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:10,630
It has been

828
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:13,620
three days since the Mount Bei incident.

829
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:16,030
The city gate is sealed,
and so is the palace gate.

830
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:17,630
We have no access to any news.

831
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:20,070
So, our only chance lies in

832
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:22,960
tomorrow's morning court session.

833
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:23,630
Yes.

834
00:37:24,710 --> 00:37:26,040
You m-made a good point.

835
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:28,920
But you're injured now, Er Lan.

836
00:37:29,070 --> 00:37:30,670
You shouldn't risk attending court
tomorrow.

837
00:37:30,670 --> 00:37:32,200
Just leave it to me and Yang.

838
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,190
What is with you, Li?

839
00:37:34,190 --> 00:37:36,320
After just promising to keep my secret,

840
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,780
you're giving it away now?

841
00:37:39,070 --> 00:37:39,510
I-I'm not.

842
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:41,510
I haven't disclosed it to anyone...

843
00:37:41,710 --> 00:37:42,880
If I were a man,

844
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:45,540
would I make a fuss
over a minor injury like this?

845
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:48,030
Yes.

846
00:37:48,670 --> 00:37:49,070
Right.

847
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:50,650
Although you

848
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:51,590
and Her Highness

849
00:37:51,590 --> 00:37:52,280
are women,

850
00:37:52,590 --> 00:37:53,920
you two are incredibly formidable.

851
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:54,880
I admire both of you.

852
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:55,880
I tip my hat to you.

853
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:59,810
Who am I to be compared with Her Highness?

854
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:02,760
I wonder

855
00:38:03,510 --> 00:38:05,310
where Her Highness is right now.

856
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,260
Your Highness!

857
00:38:13,270 --> 00:38:14,130
Your Highness.

858
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:14,920
Your Highness,

859
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:16,000
we made it back alive.

860
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:16,800
Chu Yi, Chu Si.

861
00:38:17,190 --> 00:38:18,800
Why are you dressed as Imperial Guards?

862
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,330
That gave me quite a fright!

863
00:38:22,190 --> 00:38:23,120
You're injured?

864
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,760
If I hadn't knocked out
two Imperial Guards in the chaos

865
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,020
and put on their armor,

866
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:28,820
he would've lost his arm.

867
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:30,710
Could those lousy fighters have wounded me

868
00:38:30,710 --> 00:38:31,630
if I hadn't took

869
00:38:31,790 --> 00:38:32,850
that blade for you?

870
00:38:33,100 --> 00:38:33,510
You...

871
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:34,230
Cut it out.

872
00:38:34,670 --> 00:38:36,150
What's the situation like?

873
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:37,070
Not good.

874
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:39,710
People are searching everywhere
for Her Highness.

875
00:38:39,710 --> 00:38:42,040
We absolutely cannot take the main roads.

876
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,800
But the distance between here

877
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:46,260
and Peiyang is over 500 li.

878
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:49,110
What route can we take
if not the main roads?

879
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:50,590
After living in the palace for so long,

880
00:38:50,590 --> 00:38:52,990
we're not familiar with the roads outside.

881
00:39:08,670 --> 00:39:09,470
Do you mean...

882
00:39:09,990 --> 00:39:11,120
you can be our guide?

883
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:18,250
You know the way?

884
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:20,960
Terrific.

885
00:39:22,230 --> 00:39:22,630
But...

886
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:25,180
you might get in danger

887
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,480
for sticking with us.

888
00:39:26,590 --> 00:39:27,850
Will you still join us?

889
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:35,960
You want payment?

890
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:41,960
Chu Wu,

891
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:43,090
give her some food.

892
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:44,240
By the way,

893
00:39:44,590 --> 00:39:46,050
I don't know your name yet.

894
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:52,600
You don't have a name?

895
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:57,070
Why do none of you

896
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,630
have names?

897
00:40:03,630 --> 00:40:04,090
Well...

898
00:40:05,550 --> 00:40:07,010
How about I give you a name?

899
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:12,530
Let me think...

900
00:40:23,190 --> 00:40:23,990
We'll call you

901
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,000
"Flower."

902
00:40:25,190 --> 00:40:25,650
What do you think?
